## Description

The project uses the Django REST framework to create a prediction API. The prediction API uses the model.joblib and the vectorize.joblib files which are the logistic regression model and the vectorizers, daved to file after the model training. Details on the model training are in the [Sentiment Prediction DS](https://github.com/agvar/Prediction_Text/tree/master/Sentiment_Prediction_DS) folder.

## Installation

git clone git@github.com:agvar/Prediction_Text.git

cd Prediction_API/

python -m venv venv

# Activate the virtual environment and pip install from the requirements.txt

pip install -r requirements.txt

## Steps to create a django project and run the django website locally

# Start a django project named Prediction_Text

django-admin startproject Prediction_API

# The folowig folders are created

~/Prediction_API
|-- Prediction_API
| |-- **init**.py
| |-- settings.py
| |-- urls.py
| `-- wsgi.py `-- manage.py

cd Prediction_API
python manage.py runserver

# In a web browser, open http://127.0.0.1:8000/ to view the site.

